{"type": "article", "id": 6334, "title": "Catch Me 纸抽", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-16T07:39:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052343518lJsCY26uzeSqpf7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t感冒的人应该会有过这样的体会，如果不开灯的话，半夜起来想要找纸巾，却是两眼抓瞎。西班牙设计师 Alba Garcia Molinas、Marta Zabala 与 Alex Buxens 为了解决这一可能出现的窘况，设计了一款配置了背景光的半包围式纸抽 Catch Me ，当然需要救急时它还可以扮演小台灯的角色。Catch Me 是用可丽耐材料制成，一端有一个十字形的切口，另一端装有一个微型的 LED 照明灯，造型极尽简单。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052343497JVOWZxvr26gLUzk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234349Ds9edwMftc4lW8ui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234350hsiXuI0rySbAoRDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}